dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data represents roads for Eau Claire County, Wisconsin in 2019. [This geodatabase feature class contains line features for each road centerline within Eau Claire County, WI. The data functions as a critical component of the E911 dispatch system as well as a base layer for geographic analysis and mapping. The data is maintained jointly by Eau Claire County and the City of Eau Claire.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
